Text:
I'm no audiophile, but the Moonlight Sonata track is not what I expected.  It is the 2nd movement only.  I was hoping to hear to more popular 1st movement, which is what most people associate with the title "Moonlight Sonata".  See Wikipedia for samples:
http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Moonlight_Sonata

This is no fault of the uploader, which BTW thanks for the upload, I just wish the recording companies would clarify what they put in their releases.
What is the bit depth/ sample rate, and how many channels?
Thank you, will try it out on the new AVR-4311
